Subject: Larval Writers Panel
Description: Sometimes panels with very successful writers on them are intimidating or a bit non-applicable to folks just dipping their toes in the ink, so to speak. This panel has writers struggling to find success sharing their triumphs, woes, insights, and experiences with other aspiring writers.  Speakers include:Jen Haeger, Brent Seth, Rachel Acks, Patty Templeton, Clarence Young, Skeeter Enright, Michael Elliott - Track: Literature  - Duration: 50 minutes - Audio/video needs: none
